                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. High chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Light winds becoming north to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 10 with daytime temperatures reaching the low to mid 20s.</text>
