                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Winds westerly 15 to 20 km/h tending west to southwesterly 25 to 40 km/h during the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to around 14 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
